ath d=\"m12 5 7 7-7 7\"></path></svg><a class=\"block shrink-0\" href=\"/curriculum/basic\"><div class=\"flex flex-col items-center gap-0.5 px-6 py-2 rounded-xl transition-all cursor-pointer hover:bg-slate-50 dark:hover:bg-white/5 text-slate-400\"><span class=\"text-xs font-black text-slate-400\">2. 기초</span><span class=\"text-[12px] whitespace-nowrap text-slate-400\">System &amp; Structure</span></div></a><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-arrow-right w-4 h-4 text-slate-200 shrink-0\"><path d=\"M5 12h14\"></path><path d=\"m12 5 7 7-7 7\"></path></svg><a class=\"block shrink-0\" href=\"/curriculum/practice\"><div class=\"flex flex-col items-center gap-0.5 px-6 py-2 rounded-xl transition-all cursor-pointer hover:bg-slate-50 dark:hover:bg-white/5 text-slate-400\"><span class=\"text-xs font-black text-slate-400\">3. 실전</span><span class=\"text-[12px] whitespace-nowrap text-slate-400\">Execution &amp; Build</span></div></a><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-arrow-right w-4 h-4 text-slate-200 shrink-0\"><path d=\"M5 12h14\"></path><path d=\"m12 5 7 7-7 7\"></path></svg><a class=\"block shrink-0\" href=\"/curriculum/advanced\"><div class=\"flex flex-col items-center gap-0.5 px-6 py-2 rounded-xl transition-all cursor-pointer hover:bg-slate-50 dark:hover:bg-white/5 text-slate-400\"><span class=\"text-xs font-black text-slate-400\">4. 심화</span><span class=\"text-[12px] whitespace-nowrap text-slate-400\">Scale &amp; Real World</span></div></a></div><div class=\"grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-12 gap-8 items-start\"><aside class=\"lg:col-span-3 space-y-6 sticky top-24\"><div class=\"bg-card rounded-2xl border border-border overflow-hidden shadow-sm transition-colors text-left\"><div class=\"p-5 border-b border-border bg-slate-50/50 dark:bg-slate-800/50 flex flex-col gap-1 transition-colors\"><h3 class=\"text-sm font-black text-slate-800 dark:text-white flex items-center gap-2\"><span class=\"bg-primary text-white w-5 h-5 rounded flex items-center justify-center text-[12px]\">1</span>입문 단계</h3><p class=\"text-[12px] text-primary font-bold\">&quot;AI를 제대로 쓰기 시작하는 단계&quot;</p></div><div class=\"divide-y divide-border\"><div class=\"p-4 flex items-center justify-between cursor-pointer transition-all bg-primary/10 border-r-4 border-primary \"><span class=\"font-bold transition-colors text-xs text-primary\">핵심 주제 (Core)</span><div class=\"w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-primary\"></div></div><div class=\"flex flex-col\"><div class=\"p-4 flex items-center justify-between cursor-pointer transition-all hover:bg-slate-50 dark:hover:bg-white/5 \"><span class=\"font-bold transition-colors text-xs text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400\">선택형 실습 트랙</span></div><div class=\"bg-slate-50/50 dark:bg-white/5 py-1\"><div class=\"p-4 flex items-center justify-between cursor-pointer transition-all hover:bg-slate-50 dark:hover:bg-white/5 pl-9 py-2.5\"><span class=\"font-bold transition-colors text-[12px] text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400\">트랙 A: 웹 기초 체험</span></div><div class=\"p-4 flex items-center justify-between cursor-pointer transition-all hover:bg-slate-50 dark:hover:bg-white/5 pl-9 py-2.5\"><span class=\"font-bold transition-colors text-[12px] text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400\">트랙 B: 콘텐츠 생성</span></div><div class=\"p-4 flex items-center justify-between cursor-pointer transition-all hover:bg-slate-50 dark:hover:bg-white/5 pl-9 py-2.5\"><span class=\"font-bold transition-colors text-[12px] text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400\">트랙 C: 업무 자동화</span></div></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bg-card rounded-2xl border border-border p-6 space-y-6 shadow-sm transition-colors text-left\"><div class=\"flex justify-between items-center\"><h3 class=\"font-bold text-sm text-slate-800 dark:text-white flex items-center gap-2\"><span class=\"text-lg\">🎁</span> 실습 선택 가이드</h3></div><div class=\"space-y-5\"><div class=\"space-y-2\"><p class=\"text-[12px] font-black text-indigo-500 uppercase tracking-widest\">트랙 A 선택 시</p><ul class=\"space-y-1.5\"><li class=\"flex items-start gap-2 group cursor-default\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-circle-check w-3 h-3 text-green-500 mt-0.5 shrink-0 transition-transform group-hover:scale-125\"><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"10\"></circle><path d=\"m9 12 2 2 4-4\"></path></svg><span class=\"text-[12px] font-medium text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400 group-hover:text-slate-800 dark:group-hover:text-slate-200 transition-colors leading-tight\">내가 만든 첫 웹페이지 완성</span></li><li class=\"flex items-start gap-2 group cursor-default\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-circle-check w-3 h-3 text-green-500 mt-0.5 shrink-0 transition-transform group-hover:scale-125\"><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"10\"></circle><path d=\"m9 12 2 2 4-4\"></path></svg><span class=\"text-[12px] font-medium text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400 group-hover:text-slate-800 dark:group-hover:text-slate-200 transition-colors leading-tight\">UI 요청하는 감각 습득</span></li></ul></div><div class=\"h-[1px] bg-border\"></div><div class=\"space-y-2\"><p class=\"text-[12px] font-black text-teal-500 uppercase tracking-widest\">트랙 B 선택 시</p><ul class=\"space-y-1.5\"><li class=\"flex items-start gap-2 group cursor-default\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-circle-check w-3 h-3 text-green-500 mt-0.5 shrink-0 transition-transform group-hover:scale-125\"><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"10\"></circle><path d=\"m9 12 2 2 4-4\"></path></svg><span class=\"text-[12px] font-medium text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400 group-hover:text-slate-800 dark:group-hover:text-slate-200 transition-colors leading-tight\">콘텐츠 자동 생성 구조 이해</span></li><li class=\"flex items-start gap-2 group cursor-default\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-circle-check w-3 h-3 text-green-500 mt-0.5 shrink-0 transition-transform group-hover:scale-125\"><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"10\"></circle><path d=\"m9 12 2 2 4-4\"></path></svg><span class=\"text-[12px] font-medium text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400 group-hover:text-slate-800 dark:group-hover:text-slate-200 transition-colors leading-tight\">AI 활용 루틴 구축</span></li></ul></div><div class=\"h-[1px] bg-border\"></div><div class=\"space-y-2\"><p class=\"text-[12px] font-black text-orange-500 uppercase tracking-widest\">트랙 C 선택 시</p><ul class=\"space-y-1.5\"><li class=\"flex items-start gap-2 group cursor-default\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-circle-check w-3 h-3 text-green-500 mt-0.5 shrink-0 transition-transform group-hover:scale-125\"><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"10\"></circle><path d=\"m9 12 2 2 4-4\"></path></svg><span class=\"text-[12px] font-medium text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400 group-hover:text-slate-800 dark:group-hover:text-slate-200 transition-colors leading-tight\">반복 작업 자동화 경험</span></li><li class=\"flex items-start gap-2 group cursor-default\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-circle-check w-3 h-3 text-green-500 mt-0.5 shrink-0 transition-transform group-hover:scale-125\"><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"10\"></circle><path d=\"m9 12 2 2 4-4\"></path></svg><span class=\"text-[12px] font-medium text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400 group-hover:text-slate-800 dark:group-hover:text-slate-200 transition-colors leading-tight\">실무 생산성 향상</span></li></ul></div></div></div></aside><div class=\"lg:col-span-9 space-y-16\"><div class=\"bg-card rounded-2xl border border-border p-8 shadow-sm space-y-12 transition-colors\"><div class=\"flex flex-col md:flex-row justify-between items-start gap-4 pb-8 border-b border-border text-left\"><div class=\"space-y-3\"><div class=\"flex items-center gap-2\"><span class=\"bg-primary/10 text-primary text-[12px] font-black px-2 py-0.5 rounded-full uppercase tracking-widest\">Mindset &amp; Communication</span></div><h2 class=\"text-3xl font-black text-slate-800 dark:text-white tracking-tight\">1. 입문: AI 바이브 잡기</h2><p class=\"text-primary font-bold text-lg leading-relaxed max-w-2xl\">&quot;AI를 제대로 쓰기 시작하는 단계&quot;</p><p class=\"text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400 text-sm\">코딩 실력 이전에 AI와 소통하는 법(Mindset)을 먼저 익힙니다.<br/>명확한 지시가 어떻게 드라마틱한 결과의 차이를 만드는지 직접 경험해보세요.</p></div></div><div id=\"core\" class=\"scroll-mt-32 space-y-6 text-left\"><div class=\"flex items-center gap-3\"><div class=\"w-10 h-10 rounded-xl bg-indigo-50 dark:bg-indigo-500/10 flex items-center justify-center text-indigo-600 dark:text-indigo-400\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-pen-line\"><path d=\"M12 20h9\"></path><path d=\"M16.376 3.622a1 1 0 0 1 3.002 3.002L7.368 18.635a2 2 0 0 1-.855.506l-2.872.838a.5.5 0 0 1-.62-.62l.838-2.872a2 2 0 0 1 .506-.854z\"></path></svg></div><h3 class=\"text-xl font-black text-slate-800 dark:text-white\">핵심 주제 (Common Core)</h3></div><div class=\"grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-4\"><div class=\"bg-slate-50 dark:bg-white/5 p-5 rounded-2xl border border-slate-100 dark:border-white/5 hover:border-primary/30 transition-all flex items-start gap-4 group\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-circle-check w-5 h-5 text-primary mt-0.5 shrink-0\"><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"10\"></circle><path d=\"m9 12 2 2 4-4\"></path></svg><div><h4 class=\"text-sm font-bold text-slate-800 dark:text-white mb-1 group-hover:text-primary transition-colors\">웹페이지 작동원리 이해하기</h4><p class=\"text-[12px] text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400 leading-relaxed\">브라우저와 서버가 어떻게 대화하는지 웹의 기본 흐름 파악</p></div></div><div class=\"bg-slate-50 dark:bg-white/5 p-5 rounded-2xl border border-slate-100 dark:border-white/5 hover:border-primary/30 transition-all flex items-start gap-4 group\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-circle-check w-5 h-5 text-primary mt-0.5 shrink-0\"><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"10\"></circle><path d=\"m9 12 2 2 4-4\"></path></svg><div><h4 class=\"text-sm font-bold text-slate-800 dark:text-white mb-1 group-hover:text-primary transition-colors\">바이브 코딩 개념 이해</h4><p class=\"text-[12px] text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400 leading-relaxed\">코딩을 넘어 AI에게 지시하는 새로운 개발 패러다임 이해</p></div></div><div class=\"bg-slate-50 dark:bg-white/5 p-5 rounded-2xl border border-slate-100 dark:border-white/5 hover:border-primary/30 transition-all flex items-start gap-4 group\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-circle-check w-5 h-5 text-primary mt-0.5 shrink-0\"><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"10\"></circle><path d=\"m9 12 2 2 4-4\"></path></svg><div><h4 class=\"text-sm font-bold text-slate-800 dark:text-white mb-1 group-hover:text-primary transition-colors\">바이브코딩 툴 종류와 설치하기</h4><p class=\"text-[12px] text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400 leading-relaxed\">효율적인 개발을 위한 최적의 AI 도구 세팅 및 환경 구축</p></div></div><div class=\"bg-slate-50 dark:bg-white/5 p-5 rounded-2xl border border-slate-100 dark:border-white/5 hover:border-primary/30 transition-all flex items-start gap-4 group\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-circle-check w-5 h-5 text-primary mt-0.5 shrink-0\"><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"10\"></circle><path d=\"m9 12 2 2 4-4\"></path></svg><div><h4 class=\"text-sm font-bold text-slate-800 dark:text-white mb-1 group-hover:text-primary transition-colors\">프롬프트 구조 설계</h4><p class=\"text-[12px] text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400 leading-relaxed\">역할(Role) / 목표(Goal) / 제약(Constraints)의 3요소 마스터</p></div></div><div class=\"bg-slate-50 dark:bg-white/5 p-5 rounded-2xl border border-slate-100 dark:border-white/5 hover:border-primary/30 transition-all flex items-start gap-4 group\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-circle-check w-5 h-5 text-primary mt-0.5 shrink-0\"><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"10\"></circle><path d=\"m9 12 2 2 4-4\"></path></svg><div><h4 class=\"text-sm font-bold text-slate-800 dark:text-white mb-1 group-hover:text-primary transition-colors\">명시도(구체성) 훈련</h4><p class=\"text-[12px] text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400 leading-relaxed\">AI가 오해하지 않도록 정확하게 의도를 기술하는 연습</p></div></div><div class=\"bg-slate-50 dark:bg-white/5 p-5 rounded-2xl border border-slate-100 dark:border-white/5 hover:border-primary/30 transition-all flex items-start gap-4 group\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-circle-check w-5 h-5 text-primary mt-0.5 shrink-0\"><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"10\"></circle><path d=\"m9 12 2 2 4-4\"></path></svg><div><h4 class=\"text-sm font-bold text-slate-800 dark:text-white mb-1 group-hover:text-primary transition-colors\">실패 vs 성공 요청 분석</h4><p class=\"text-[12px] text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400 leading-relaxed\">왜 AI가 엉뚱한 대답을 하는지 케이스 스터디</p></div></div><div class=\"bg-slate-50 dark:bg-white/5 p-5 rounded-2xl border border-slate-100 dark:border-white/5 hover:border-primary/30 transition-all flex items-start gap-4 group\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-circle-check w-5 h-5 text-primary mt-0.5 shrink-0\"><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"10\"></circle><path d=\"m9 12 2 2 4-4\"></path></svg><div><h4 class=\"text-sm font-bold text-slate-800 dark:text-white mb-1 group-hover:text-primary transition-colors\">일반 vs 특수 요청 구분</h4><p class=\"text-[12px] text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400 leading-relaxed\">상황에 맞는 최적의 소통 방식(One-shot, Few-shot 등) 선택</p></div></div></div></div><div class=\"pt-4 border-t border-border text-left\"><div class=\"flex items-center gap-3 mb-6\"><div class=\"w-10 h-10 rounded-xl bg-teal-50 dark:bg-teal-500/10 flex items-center justify-center text-teal-600 dark:text-teal-400\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-zap\"><path d=\"M4 14a1 1 0 0 1-.78-1.63l9.9-10.2a.5.5 0 0 1 .86.46l-1.92 6.02A1 1 0 0 0 13 10h7a1 1 0 0 1 .78 1.63l-9.9 10.2a.5.5 0 0 1-.86-.46l1.92-6.02A1 1 0 0 0 11 14z\"></path></svg></div><h3 class=\"text-xl font-black text-slate-800 dark:text-white\">선택형 실습 트랙 (Optional Tracks)</h3></div><p class=\"text-sm text-slate-500 mb-10\">본인의 목표에 맞는 트랙을 선택하여 실습을 진행하세요. (중복 선택 가능)</p><div class=\"space-y-12\"><div id=\"track-a\" class=\"scroll-mt-32 bg-white dark:bg-slate-900 rounded-3xl border-2 border-indigo-100 dark:border-indigo-500/20 p-8 space-y-6 hover:border-primary transition-all group shadow-sm\"><div class=\"flex justify-between items-center\"><div class=\"inline-flex bg-indigo-50 dark:bg-indigo-500/10 text-indigo-600 dark:text-indigo-400 text-[12px] font-black px-3 py-1 rounded-full uppercase tracking-widest\">Track A</div><div class=\"flex items-center gap-2 text-xs font-bold text-slate-400\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"14\" height=\"14\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-clock text-indigo-400\"><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"10\"></circle><polyline points=\"12 6 12 12 16 14\"></polyline></svg> 예상 60분</div></div><div><h4 class=\"text-2xl font-black text-slate-800 dark:text-white mb-2\">웹 기초 체험</h4><p class=\"text-sm text-slate-500 leading-relaxed\">직접 눈에 보이는 화면을 설계하며 AI와의 소통 결과를 즉각적으로 확인합니다.</p></div><div class=\"grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-4 pt-2\"><div class=\"bg-slate-50 dark:bg-white/5 p-4 rounded-xl border border-slate-100 dark:border-white/5\"><p class=\"text-xs font-bold mb-2\">실습 01. 랜딩페이지</p><p class=\"text-[12px] text-slate-500 leading-relaxed\">AI에게 지시하여 10분 만에 근사한 웹사이트 뼈대를 구축합니다.</p></div><div class=\"bg-slate-50 dark:bg-white/5 p-4 rounded-xl border border-slate-100 dark:border-white/5\"><p class=\"text-xs font-bold mb-2\">실습 02. UI 요청 최적화</p><p class=\"text-[12px] text-slate-500 leading-relaxed\">추상적인 요청이 아닌 정교한 지시어로 UI 레이아웃을 수정합니다.</p></div></div><button class=\"w-full py-4 bg-slate-900 dark:bg-white/10 text-white font-black rounded-2xl hover:bg-primary transition-all shadow-xl shadow-slate-900/10 hover:shadow-primary/25\">웹 트랙 실습 시작하기</button></div><div id=\"track-b\" class=\"scroll-mt-32 bg-white dark:bg-slate-900 rounded-3xl border-2 border-teal-100 dark:border-teal-500/20 p-8 space-y-6 hover:border-primary transition-all group shadow-sm\"><div class=\"flex justify-between items-center\"><div class=\"inline-flex bg-teal-50 dark:bg-teal-500/10 text-teal-600 dark:text-teal-400 text-[12px] font-black px-3 py-1 rounded-full uppercase tracking-widest\">Track B</div><div class=\"flex items-center gap-2 text-xs font-bold text-slate-400\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"14\" height=\"14\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-clock text-teal-400\"><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"10\"></circle><polyline points=\"12 6 12 12 16 14\"></polyline></svg> 예상 40분</div></div><div><h4 class=\"text-2xl font-black text-slate-800 dark:text-white mb-2\">콘텐츠 생성</h4><p class=\"text-sm text-slate-500 leading-relaxed\">마케터나 기획자처럼 AI를 활용하여 고품질의 콘텐츠 생산 체계를 구축합니다.</p></div><div class=\"grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-4 pt-2\"><div class=\"bg-slate-50 dark:bg-white/5 p-4 rounded-xl border border-slate-100 dark:border-white/5\"><p class=\"text-xs font-bold mb-2\">실습 01. 블로그 자동화</p><p class=\"text-[12px] text-slate-500 leading-relaxed\">특정 주제에 대해 AI가 논리적이고 풍부한 글을 쓰도록 지시합니다.</p></div><div class=\"bg-slate-50 dark:bg-white/5 p-4 rounded-xl border border-slate-100 dark:border-white/5\"><p class=\"text-xs font-bold mb-2\">실습 02. 이미지 &amp; 카피</p><p class=\"text-[12px] text-slate-500 leading-relaxed\">시선을 끄는 썸네일 설명과 광고 카피를 생성하는 프롬프트를 만듭니다.</p></div></div><button class=\"w-full py-4 bg-slate-900 dark:bg-white/10 text-white font-black rounded-2xl hover:bg-primary transition-all shadow-xl shadow-slate-900/10 hover:shadow-primary/25\">콘텐츠 트랙 실습 시작하기</button></div><div id=\"track-c\" class=\"scroll-mt-32 bg-white dark:bg-slate-900 rounded-3xl border-2 border-orange-100 dark:border-orange-500/20 p-8 space-y-6 hover:border-primary transition-all group shadow-sm text-left\"><div class=\"flex justify-between items-center\"><div class=\"inline-flex bg-orange-50 dark:bg-orange-500/10 text-orange-600 dark:text-orange-400 text-[12px] font-black px-3 py-1 rounded-full uppercase tracking-widest\">Track C</div><div class=\"flex items-center gap-2 text-xs font-bold text-slate-400\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"14\" height=\"14\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-clock text-orange-400\"><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"10\"></circle><polyline points=\"12 6 12 12 16 14\"></polyline></svg> 예상 50분</div></div><div><h4 class=\"text-2xl font-black text-slate-800 dark:text-white mb-2\">업무 자동화</h4><p class=\"text-sm text-slate-500 leading-relaxed\">단순 반복 업무를 AI에게 맡기고 생산성을 극대화하는 방법을 실습합니다.</p></div><div class=\"grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-4 pt-2\"><div class=\"bg-slate-50 dark:bg-white/5 p-4 rounded-xl border border-slate-100 dark:border-white/5\"><p class=\"text-xs font-bold mb-2\">실습 01. 업무 템플릿</p><p class=\"text-[12px] text-slate-500 leading-relaxed\">주간 보고, 이메일 답장 등 반복되는 문서의 표준 프롬프트를 제작합니다.</p></div><div class=\"bg-slate-50 dark:bg-white/5 p-4 rounded-xl border border-slate-100 dark:border-white/5\"><p class=\"text-xs font-bold mb-2\">실습 02. 문서 자동 요약</p><p class=\"text-[12px] text-slate-500 leading-relaxed\">긴 회의록이나 보고서를 핵심 위주로 요약하고 Action Item을 추출합니다.</p></div></div><button class=\"w-full py-4 bg-slate-900 dark:bg-white/10 text-white font-black rounded-2xl hover:bg-primary transition-all shadow-xl shadow-slate-900/10 hover:shadow-primary/25\">자동화 트랙 실습 시작하기</button></div></div></div><div class=\"pt-8 border-t border-border flex justify-end\"><a href=\"/curriculum/basic\"><button class=\"bg-primary text-white px-8 py-3 rounded-xl font-bold flex items-center gap-2 hover:bg-indigo-500 transition-all hover:scale-105 shadow-lg shadow-primary/20\">2. 기초 단계: 시스템 사고 <svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-chevron-right w-4 h-4\"><path d=\"m9 18 6-6-6-6\"></path></svg></button></a></div></div></div></div></main></div></div><footer class=\"bg-slate-50 dark:bg-slate-900/50 border-t border-border pt-16 pb-8\"><div class=\"max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6\"><div class=\"grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 mb-12\"><div class=\"footer-brand\"><a class=\"flex items-center gap-2 font-bold text-lg mb-4 hover:text-primary transition-colors text-foreground\" href=\"/\"><svg width=\"22\" height=\"16.785185185185185\" viewBox=\"0 0 81 61.8\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" class=\"\" id=\"vibe-logo-svg\"><path fill=\"#D7D7D7\" d=\"M30 59H20c-9 0-17-8-17-17V3s5 11 22 11S47 3 47 3v39c0 9-8 17-17 17z\"></path><path fill=\"#ef4444\" d=\"M61 59H32s5 0 10-6 5-11 5-11V3h31v39c0 9-7 17-17 17z\"></path><path fill=\"currentColor\" style=\"color:var(--foreground);transition:color 0.3s ease\" d=\"M20 62C9 62 0 53 0 42V3a3 3 0 0 1 6 0v39c0 7 6 14 14 14a3 3 0 1 1 0 6zM30 62a3 3 0 1 1 0-6c7 0 14-7 14-14V3a3 3 0 1 1 6 0v39c0 11-9 20-20 20zM61 62a3 3 0 1 1 0-6c8 0 14-7 14-14V3a3 3 0 1 1 6 0v39c0 11-9 20-20 20z\"></path></svg><span>엘쯔의 바이브코딩</span></a><p class=\"text-sm opacity-60 leading-relaxed max-w-sm text-foreground\">UX디자인, 퍼블리싱, 프런트엔드 개발 지식을 공유하고<br/>함께 성장하는 바이브 코딩 스터디 공간입니다.</p></div><div class=\"flex gap-16 md:justify-end\"><div class=\"flex flex-col gap-3\"><h4 class=\"text-xs font-black uppercase tracking-widest opacity-40 mb-2 text-foreground\">사이트</h4><a class=\"text-sm opacity-60 hover:opacity-100 hover:text-primary transition-all text-foreground\" href=\"/curriculum\">커리큘럼</a><a class=\"text-sm opacity-60 hover:opacity-100 hover:text-primary transition-all text-foreground\" href=\"/practice\">기능실습</a><a class=\"text-sm opacity-60 hover:opacity-100 hover:text-primary transition-all text-foreground\" href=\"/resources\">자료실</a><a class=\"text-sm opacity-60 hover:opacity-100 hover:text-primary transition-all text-foreground\" href=\"/guide\">사전학습</a></div><div class=\"flex flex-col gap-3\"><h4 class=\"text-xs font-black uppercase tracking-widest opacity-40 mb-2 text-foreground\">지원</h4><a class=\"text-sm opacity-60 hover:opacity-100 hover:text-primary transition-all text-foreground\" href=\"/faq\">자주하는 질문</a><a class=\"text-sm opacity-60 hover:opacity-100 hover:text-primary transition-all text-foreground\" href=\"/contact\">문의하기</a><a class=\"text-sm opacity-60 hover:opacity-100 hover:text-primary transition-all text-foreground\" href=\"/terms\">이용약관</a><a class=\"text-sm opacity-60 hover:opacity-100 hover:text-primary transition-all text-foreground\" href=\"/privacy\">개인정보처리방침</a></div></div></div><div class=\"pt-8 border-t border-border flex flex-col sm:flex-row justify-between items-center gap-6\"><p class=\"text-xs opacity-40 font-medium text-foreground\">© <!-- -->2026<!-- --> 엘쯔의 바이브코딩. All rights reserved.</p><button class=\"w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-white dark:bg-slate-800 border border-border shadow-sm flex items-center justify-center text-foreground hover:border-primary hover:text-primary transition-all group\" aria-label=\"맨 위로\" id=\"scroll-to-top\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"18\" height=\"18\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" str